{"tid":244132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高估台網民收入？ 網傳黑客免費解鎖","createTime":"2017-05-15T07:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T14:22:09.000Z","uid":95520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e6809ab4463968b49fdd0fb4951fe17ffca37d9","tid":244132,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:50:28.000Z","msg":"全球大量電腦遭黑客發放的「WannaCry」病毒攻擊，要求繳付數百美元的比特幣以恢復檔案。可是，有台灣網民被另一款病毒ThunderCrypt攻擊，鎖死電腦後，竟然去信黑客投訴他們收得太貴，沒想到黑客竟然回信，稱「高估台灣人的收入」，並免費為網民解鎖。黑客獲台灣網民大讚，稱他們「有佛心」，更比台灣企業客服好太多！<br />\n<br />\n這名網民將他的經歷放在fb群組，稱他在打電腦遊戲時發現「中招」，黑客要求他付0.345比特幣，相當於4,842港元的「贖款」，才會為他的電腦解鎖。　<br />\n<br />\n網民不但沒有付款，更去信黑客，稱「我每月收入才400美元（約3,120港元），你真的要這樣對我嗎」，沒想到黑客竟然回信，稱「老實說我們似乎過於高估你們台灣的收入了」，並認為他們對台灣的策略是「完全失敗」，黑客不用網民付錢，便為他電腦解鎖。<br />\n<br />\n當然，黑客亦向網民稱：「如果你喜歡我們，並且有意請我們喝幾杯咖啡的話，我們永遠歡迎的！」<br />\n<br />\n有網民稱這些黑客做法，「值得很多企業學習」，更稱這些黑客「大陸竊取遊戲物品還要來的有品多了」，不過，亦有網民不太高興，認為這是「國際認證台灣低薪國」，這次之後「台灣薪水太低，全球皆知」。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170515&amp;guid=56694805&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170515%26guid%3D56694805%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a11d8eae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170515%26guid%3D56694805%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=605d3ce8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170515&amp;guid=56694805&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"d66aff279a93ef29f3c8dfb496593786e9a2c3e8","tid":244132,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:54:50.000Z","msg":"原來窮都有好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c68fbeb35e6b956fd8527176cb874ea46d3686","tid":244132,"uid":1139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:56:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36b1ede432d1ac8045d9d0dac89bbdc36fe436a4","tid":244132,"uid":9104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:57:35.000Z","msg":"島民小確幸"},{"pid":"fbfef177fe889753d197c8cfe446b3e1551f7aca","tid":244132,"uid":69794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:00:40.000Z","msg":"如果香港人影自己住一念無明果d劏房個黑客應該會眼濕濕咁免費解鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15280e05e8ffd1eb5e4951f8e98152c8abb5b46","tid":244132,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果香港人影自己住一念無明果d劏房個黑客應該會眼濕濕咁免費解鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n劏房嘅月租分分鐘都高過台仔嘅月入啦"},{"pid":"0cc3a2ddd32402d95d94b9df97ebdcc5f2fa3b4f","tid":244132,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果香港人影自己住一念無明果d劏房個黑客應該會眼濕濕咁免費解鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲可能免費送多次電腦全機檢查<br />\n心諗：我隻狗張床仲大過香港人間屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e27311042c2b5a7484655c70151e872bd4bd9b","tid":244132,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:20:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果香港人影自己住一念無明果d劏房個黑客應該會眼濕濕咁免費解鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲可能免費送多次電腦全機檢查<br />\n心諗：我隻狗張床仲大過香港人間屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能某日速遞會有部新notebook黎謝罪道歉"},{"pid":"bb0b61775fb0d9d1e20e58bd050f07acb3d357f2","tid":244132,"uid":80457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>引用</blockquote>"},{